client
dev tun
proto udp
remote vpn.example.com 1194
resolv-retry infinite
nobind
persist-key
persist-tun
remote-cert-tls server
auth-user-pass
verb 3
<ca>
-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
MIIBFAKECERTFORTESTSONLYNOTAREALCERTIFICATEAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA
AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA
-----END CERTIFICATE-----
</ca>
